'''Aaron Silverman''' is an American chef, owner of Rose's Luxury in [[Washington, DC]].

Silverman has been the subject of a profile in the [[Washington Post]], which characterized his work as mastery of 'the art of serious play',<ref>[http://www.washingtonpost.com/lifestyle/food/roses-luxury-chef-aaron-silverman-masters-the-art-of-serious-play/2014/08/25/dfc0d674-274d-11e4-8593-da634b334390_story.html?hpid=z1 Washington Post]</ref> and Rose's Luxury has been reviewed as 'the best new restaurant in America' by [[Bon App<U+00E9>tit]].<ref>[http://www.bonappetit.com/restaurants-travel/best-new-restaurants/article/roses-luxury Bon App<U+00E9>tit, 19 August 2014]</ref>

